                    <li><strong>"User"</strong> refers to any person accessing or using our website</li>
                    <li><strong>"Products"</strong> refers to all items listed for sale on our website</li>
                    <li><strong>"Order"</strong> refers to a request to purchase products from our website</li>
                    <li><strong>"Account"</strong> refers to the user's registered profile on our website</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- User Accounts -->
            <div class="terms-section">
