                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Orders are processed within 24-48 hours</li>
                    <li>You'll receive order confirmation via Discord/Email</li>
                    <li>Payment proof required for QR code payments</li>
                    <li>Orders may be cancelled if payment not verified within 24 hours</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Shipping and Delivery -->
            <div class="terms-section">
                <h2 class="terms-title">6. Shipping and Delivery</h2>
                <p class="terms-text">
                    We offer shipping across India. Delivery times may vary based on your location and product availability.
                </p>
                
                <h3 class="terms-subtitle">Delivery Timeline:</h3>
                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Metro Cities: 3-5 business days</li>
                    <li>Tier 2 Cities: 5-7 business days</li>
                    <li>Rural Areas: 7-10 business days</li>
                    <li>Custom Products: 10-15 business days</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3 class="terms-subtitle">Shipping Charges:</h3>
                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Free shipping on orders above ₹999</li>
                    <li>₹50 shipping charge for orders below ₹999</li>
                    <li>No hidden charges</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Returns and Refunds -->
            <div class="terms-section">
                <h2 class="terms-title">7. Returns and Refunds</h2>
                <p class="terms-text">
                    We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy with your order, 
                    we offer returns under certain conditions.
                </p>
                
                <h3 class="terms-subtitle">Return Policy:</h3>
                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Returns accepted within 7 days of delivery</li>
                    <li>Items must be unused and in original packaging</li>
                    <li>Custom printed items cannot be returned unless defective</li>
                    <li>Return shipping to be borne by customer</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3 class="terms-subtitle">Refund Process:</h3>
                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Refunds processed within 5-7 business days</li>
                    <li>Amount credited to original payment method</li>
                    <li>QR code payments refunded via bank transfer</li>
                    <li>Contact support for refund status</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- User Conduct -->
            <div class="terms-section">
                <h2 class="terms-title">8. User Conduct</h2>
                <p class="terms-text">
                    You agree not to use our website for any unlawful purpose or in any way that could damage, 
                    disable, or impair our services.
                </p>
                
                <h3 class="terms-subtitle">Prohibited Activities:</h3>
                <ul class="terms-list">
                    <li>Attempting to gain unauthorized access</li>
                    <li>Using automated systems or bots</li>
                    <li>Harassing other users or staff</li>
                    <li>Posting false or misleading reviews</li>
                    <li>Engaging in fraudulent transactions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Privacy Policy -->
            <div class="terms-section">
                <h2 class="terms-title">9. Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p class="terms-text">
                    Your privacy is important to us. We collect and use your information as described in our Privacy Policy. 
                    By using our website, you consent to such collection and use.
                </p>
                
